Properties.commandText:
CREATE TABLE [Configurations] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Uri] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [DiscoveryService] nvarchar(100) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Configurations] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Executions] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [OnStateFrom] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [LastExecuted] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [Uri] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [DiscoveryService] nvarchar(50) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Executions] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Failures] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [HealthCheckName] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [LastNotified] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsUpAndRunning] bit NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Failures] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [HealthCheckExecutionEntries] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [Duration] time NOT NULL,
    [HealthCheckExecutionId] int NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_HealthCheckExecutionEntries] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_HealthCheckExecutionEntries_Executions_HealthCheckExecutionId] FOREIGN KEY ([HealthCheckExecutionId]) REFERENCES [Executions] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [HealthCheckExecutionHistories] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(50) NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [On] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [HealthCheckExecutionId] int NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_HealthCheckExecutionHistories] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_HealthCheckExecutionHistories_Executions_HealthCheckExecutionId] FOREIGN KEY ([HealthCheckExecutionId]) REFERENCES [Executions] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Configurations] AS [c]) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
